title: Neiko 50637 Hilltex Dirty Water Submersible Water Pump with Float Switch, 1/2 hp/16'
features: POWERFUL & FAST: Fully submersible and powerful electric water pump can be submerged up to 16 feet and pumps water at 1980 gallons per hour
VERSATILE: Quickly empties/transfers water from tanks, spas, koi ponds, and drains and picks up particles up to 1 3/16" in size
FLOAT SWITCH CONTROL: Easy to use float switch detects water level and can be used to turn the pump on or off as needed.
WATERPROOF: Constructed of corrosion-resistant thermoplastic, bright color is easy to spot when submerged
INCLUDES HOSE ADAPTERS: Pipe diameter measures 1¼" and pump includes adapters for ½” hoses or ¾” hoses
description: The dirty water submersible water pump is a great tool to have for moving a large amount of water from one place to another. It delivers powerful pumping at 9000 liters per hour while being able to be fully submerged at a maximum depth of 16 feet. The automatic float switch also shuts off once water level reaches 30 centimeters and the sump pump is super versatile in both clean water and dirty water operations in agricultural, horticultural, plumbing, and home uses.
